md:
giải nghĩa từ "literary" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* Literary (adjective)
	+ Meaning: relating to literature, especially written works of art.
	+ Vietnamese: văn chương, liên quan đến văn học
	+ Example sentence: "The literary critic analyzed the novel's themes and characters."
	+ Related words: literature, literary work, literary critic, literary theory

* Literary (noun)
	+ Meaning: written works of art, especially those considered to have artistic or intellectual value.
	+ Vietnamese: văn chương, tác phẩm văn học
	+ Example sentence: "The literary canon includes works by authors such as Shakespeare and Austen."
	+ Related words: literature, literary work, literary movement, literary award

Note: The word "literary" can have different meanings depending on the context in which it is used. The above definitions and examples are just a few possible interpretations of the word.
